      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BORACAY STORM (3) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 5.5 lengths win at Ballarat in a handy 21.96. Has a low draw and goes well over this trip. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Well placed and will be tough to beat. JETSTREAM ICON (1) was out of placings last time (30.97) at The Meadows in a Grade 5, finishing eighth and beaten 12 lengths. Has four wins already from this draw. Makes strong appeal on best. HOLDEN BALE (4) stuck on well last time to finish 1.5 lengths back in second (29.95) at Sandown in a Grade 5 over 515m. Expected to be in this for a long way.",
